#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:45
#: 92455e8a4b9a40a2be52642788424308
msgid ""
"Node transitions follow two rules: 1) if a :math:`S` state node has "
":math:`I` state neighbors, each :math:`I` state neighbor transmits the "
"infection to the :math:`S` state node with probability :math:`\\beta`; 2) "
"the :math:`I` state node is recovered to the :math:`R` state with "
"probability :math:`1`."
msgstr ""
"节点过渡遵循两个规则:1)如果一个:math:‘S'州节点有:math:‘I'州邻居,每个:math:‘I'州邻居将感染传染到:math:‘S'州节点有概率:`\\贝塔';2)一个:math:‘I'州节点恢复到:math:‘R'州有概率:`1'."

