msgid ""
"Node states are represented by two Boolean indicator vectors :math:`h, r "
"\\in \\{0,1\\}^N`:"
msgstr "节点状态由两个布尔指示向量表示 : “ h, r\\ in \\\\0, 1\\\\ N :"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:58
#: 4d332e1303524cdc8816ece8a2444915
msgid ":math:`h_i=1` denotes ``infected`` (**Active**)"
msgstr ":math:`h i=1'表示“感染”(**主动**)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:59
#: a1dfac67ef764bf3ae4f3004fe498d40
msgid ":math:`r_i=1` denotes ``recovered`` (**Active**)"
msgstr ":math:`r i=1'表示“已恢复”(**Act**)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:60
#: c818648d62ee4edf876d0bf4926ffb40
msgid ":math:`(h_i,r_i)=(0,0)` denotes ``susceptible`` (**Inactive**)"
msgstr ":math:`(h i,r i)=(0,0)'表示“可接受”(**不活动**)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:62
#: bedd425dc83a4ea0ae2f1f5f7802bd61
msgid ""
"The update of the system at step :math:`k` is decomposed into three stages:"
msgstr "系统分三个阶段更新:"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:64
#: 24a55645fd7b4e42813582b37d6b0670
msgid ""
"Each infected neighbor :math:`j` of node :math:`i` transmits a log-"
"probability contribution"
msgstr "每个受感染的邻居:math:节点的`j':math:`i ' 传递日志概率贡献"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:66
#: 1f165cca12c64dde85734b8d41318d96
msgid "m_{ji}^{(k)} = h_j^{(k-1)} \\cdot \\log(1-\\beta)"
msgstr "m {ji}^{(k)}=h j^{(k-1)}\\cdot\\log(1-\\β)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:71
#: 79c921a5cd8d4878919597b563c85d75
msgid ""
"Node :math:`i` collects contributions from all neighbors :math:`N(i)` to "
"compute its infection probability"
msgstr "节点: \" i \" 收集所有邻居的贡献: \" N(i) \" 计算感染概率"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:73
#: 4388d28883a8448898e514aad25a780c
msgid "m_i^{(k)} = 1 - \\exp\\!\\left( \\sum_{j \\in N(i)} m_{ji}^{(k)} \\right)"
msgstr "m i^{(k)}=1 -\\exp\\!\\左(\\sum {j\\in N(i)} m {ji}^{(k)}\\右)"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:78
#: dc4fa4a218944ce3bc444c9894322b1e
msgid ""
"The indicator variables are updated with independent uniform random "
"variables :math:`U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}}, U_i^{\\mathrm{rec}} \\sim "
"\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)`"
msgstr ""
"指标变量以独立的统一随机变量更新 : math :`U i^{\\ mathrm{inf}}, U i^{\\ "
"mathrm{rec}}\\sim\\mathrm{Uniform}(0,1)'"

#: ../../source/library/models/epidemics/IndependentCascades.rst:80
#: 74d2a823497d4ae39c53c98080c17e50
msgid ""
"\\begin{aligned}\n"
"    h_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"    \\begin{cases}\n"
"            1, & \\text{if } (h_i^{(k-1)}=0 \\land r_i^{(k-1)}=0) \\land (U_i^{\\mathrm{inf}} < m_i^{(k)}), \\\\[4pt]\n"
"            0, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=1, \\\\[4pt]\n"
"            h_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise},\n"
"    \\end{cases} \\\\[6pt]\n"
"    r_i^{(k)} &=\n"
"    \\begin{cases}\n"
"            1, & \\text{if } h_i^{(k-1)}=1, \\\\[4pt]\n"
"            r_i^{(k-1)}, & \\text{otherwise}.\n"
"    \\end{cases}\n"
"\\end{aligned}"
msgstr ""
"开始{对齐}\n"
"h(k)}\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} (h i^{(k-1)}=0\\land r i^{(k-1)}=0)\\land (U i^{\\mathrm{inf}}} < m i^{(k)}),\\\\[4pt]\n"
"0, &\\ text{if} h i^{(k-1)}=1,\\\\[4pt]\n"
"h i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类},\n"
"\\ end{ cases}\\\\\\ [6pt]\n"
"r i^{(k)}\n"
"开始{ cases}\n"
"1, &\\ text{if} h i^{(k-1)}\\\\[4pt]\n"
"r i^{(k-1)}, &\\ text{另类}.\n"
"结束{ cases}\n"
"结束{对齐}"

